---
import "../../styles/brasil/differentials.css";
---

<section class="br-diffs" id="diferenciais">
  <div class="br-diffs__inner">
    <div class="br-diffs__header" data-reveal="fade-up">
      <span class="br-diffs__tag">Diferenciais</span>
      <h2 class="br-diffs__title">
        Por que escolher a FERIOLI?
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="br-diffs__grid" data-stagger>
      <div class="br-diffs__card" data-reveal="fade-up">
        <div class="br-diffs__icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="br-diffs__card-title">Mais de 75 anos de experiência</h3>
        <p class="br-diffs__card-text">Décadas desenvolvendo equipamentos para as maiores empresas da América Latina.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="br-diffs__card" data-reveal="fade-up">
        <div class="br-diffs__icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="br-diffs__card-title">Engenharia própria</h3>
        <p class="br-diffs__card-text">Projetos desenvolvidos internamente por uma equipe altamente especializada.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="br-diffs__card" data-reveal="fade-up">
        <div class="br-diffs__icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M2 20L2 22 22 22 22 20ZM4 20L4 4 10 4 10 20ZM12 20L12 9 20 9 20 20Z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="br-diffs__card-title">Fabricação própria</h3>
        <p class="br-diffs__card-text">Controle total da qualidade durante todo o processo produtivo.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="br-diffs__card" data-reveal="fade-up">
        <div class="br-diffs__icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="br-diffs__card-title">Equipamentos de 1,5 a 92 toneladas</h3>
        <p class="br-diffs__card-text">Uma linha completa para diferentes segmentos industriais.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="br-diffs__card" data-reveal="fade-up">
        <div class="br-diffs__icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="br-diffs__card-title">Pós-venda permanente</h3>
        <p class="br-diffs__card-text">Suporte técnico, peças originais e atendimento especializado.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="br-diffs__card" data-reveal="fade-up">
        <div class="br-diffs__icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"/><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="br-diffs__card-title">Presença latino-americana</h3>
        <p class="br-diffs__card-text">Argentina, Brasil e Peru.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
